
New Features in tasksh 1.0

  - libreadline support.

New commands in tasksh 1.0

  - None

New configuration options in tasksh 1.0

  - None

Newly deprecated features in tasksh 1.0

  - None

Removed features in 1.0

  - None

Known Issues

  - None

Tasksh has been built and tested on the following configurations:

  * OS X
  * Fedora
  * Ubuntu
  * Debian
  * Arch Linux
  * FreeBSD
  * Cygwin 1.7

---

While Tasksh has undergone testing, bugs are sure to remain.  If you
encounter a bug, please enter a new issue at:

  http://bug.tasktools.org

Or you can also report the issue in the forums at:

  http://answers.tasktools.org

Or just send a message to:

  support@taskwarrior.org

Thank you.
